meaningMnemonic: Your <kanji>fate</kanji> <kanji>orders</kanji> are the orders you get from above. You are <vocabulary>order</vocabulary>ed and <vocabulary>command</vocabulary>ed to carry out said orders.
readingMnemonic: This is a jukugo word, which usually means on'yomi readings from the kanji. If you know the readings of your kanji you'll know how to read this as well.
